<h1 class='font-cmu font-bold'>YOU LOVE ENGAGING WITH MEDIA? HERE'S SOME IDEAS:</h1>
<small>these are just some random suggestions: you can do whatever YOU can and would like! also, feel free to share this for any other fandom.</small>
<h2>SHARE THE COMIC:</h2>
<ul>
<li>ask someone to read it (be kind; suggest, don&#39;t force!)</li>
<li>maybe read it together with them </li>
<li>or ask them to record their reaction</li>
<li>or make a live reaction thread</li>
<li>(author&#39;s note: reading aloud in a group with &quot;voice acting&quot; is a lot of fun!)</li>
<li>discuss it with someone</li>
<li>contribute to community-ran <a href='https://www.doesthedogdie.com/media/1605829'>content warning list</a> to make it more accessible!</li>
<li><a href='./help_us.html'>translate it</a> (or just write about it in your native language)</li>
<li><a href='./help_us.html'>transcribe it</a></li>
</ul>
<h2>SHARE YOUR THOUGHTS:</h2>
<ul>
<li>make a silly small post about it somewhere</li>
<li>or write a review (we have komments section if you want it to be on-site!)</li>
<li>or make a whole serious as hell youtube video about it</li>
<li>do anything YOU would have fun with, okay? :]</li>
</ul>

