<h2>WIKIAS:</h2>
<ul>
<li>you want to start a fan wikia?! awesome!<ul>
<li>consider using <a href='https://miraheze.org/'>MIRAHEZE</a> (in order to make a wiki, you have to ask them to lend you space for one: it sounds scary and takes a bit of time but i PROMISE it is worth it) and NOT FANDOM</li>
<li>if you do want to have some kind of simple-to-make + simple-to-edit wikia, consider making a TVtropes page (it has annoying adblocking rules BUT you don&#39;t get them if you make an account). also consider making a TVtropes page if you just like TVtropes lmao ❤️ </li>
<li>avrum is experienced with wikias: if you need some advice or help, just contact xem!</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h2>PRESERVE:</h2>
<ul>
<li>download the whole comic</li>
<li>download the whole website</li>
<li>burn it onto some kind of physical medium  </li>
<li>put it on some kind of file hosting or some type of an <a href='https://archive.org/'>internet archive</a></li>
<li>repost/rehost bits of it</li>
<li>make bits of it into paper irl comics</li>
<li>save it, any way you&#39;d like</li>
</ul>

finally,
<br>
    stay civil and avoid harassing people<br>
    know online drama cannot say anything about your worth as a human being<br>
    tag your content (derealization/suggestive/etc) if the need arises<br>
    remember that you matter and that you can take breaks from social media when it gets overwhelming<br>
	and most importantly<br>
	<b class='p-2 text-black-adapt bg-white-adapt '>have fun :]   ❤️🧡💛💚💙💜</b> <br>
  
